block content
	//- include subheader
	main#projects
		h1
			| Projects
		h2
			a(href="#codemagic")
			| Codemagic
		p
			| Codemagic.gr is a powerful online code editor for web development! It's open-source and it follows the philosophy of client-side and fast execution. It's built for creative people who do a lot of web-related experiments and want to test stuff in real-time without the hassle of preparing project files and whatnot. It is also a great place for people to come and learn various web-technologies like HTML, CSS, JS and their derivatives.
		p
			a(href="http://codemagic.gr")
				| [site]
			| ,&nbsp;
			a(href="https://github.com/varemenos/codemagic")
				| [source]

		h2
			a(href="#verepo")
			| veRepo
		p
			| veRepo is an open source SASS library of modules and mixins for robust and maintainable front-end development using SASS. Most of the modular items/objects in this repo will work by just adding 1 class name to the html element you desire to style (although there are some exceptions).
		p
			a(href="http://varemenos.github.io/verepo")
				| [site]
			| ,&nbsp;
			a(href="https://github.com/varemenos/verepo")
				| [source]
			| ,&nbsp;
