		p
			| A digital playground to explore the capabilities of Sass.js.
		p
			a(href="http://medialize.github.io/playground.sass.js/")
				| [site]
			| ,&nbsp;
			a(href="https://github.com/medialize/playground.sass.js")
				| [source]

		h2
			a(href="#docfinder")
			| docFinder
