			| An open source Documentation Searching webapp using searchco.de's API which provides documentation for languages like Apache 2, GIT, GNU/Linux Commands, HTTP Codes, Java, Javascript, JQuery, MySQL, Nginx, Perl 5, PHP, Python, Underscore.js, VB 6 and more.
